# Repo guardrails

- Read `AGENTS.md` first for path ownership; do not paste full READMEs into context.
- Never commit secrets (`.env`, `.tfvars`, OCI keys, Docker Hub tokens).
- Prefer small patches over broad refactors.
- Stack is OCI OKE + Cilium/Hubble + Gateway API — not AWS EKS, not Istio/Kiali.
- Worker nodes are ARM64 Always Free; keep multi-arch or arm64 images.
- Frontend image tags are set by CI (`kubectl set image`); leave placeholder tags in manifests.
